The '''crimson-crowned flowerpecker''' ('''''Dicaeum nehrkorni''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Dicaeidae]]. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to the island of [[Sulawesi]] in [[Indonesia]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]] and subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]].

